Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,### 前奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(475,450)\blur1}看，月光灑下，在其中的同志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\blur1}我們什麼東西都不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\blur1}看，戰爭令下，在這樣的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,300)\blur1}我們什麼退路都已經沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,450)\blur1}對著這黑夜，對著這明月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.19,0:00:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\blur1}發誓你將會付出你所有擁有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,850)\blur1}為永恆的黑夜，為無盡的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(330,850)\blur1}正是時候...
Comment: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,### 導歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:01:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,900)\blur1}請為了你們未來，做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,150)\blur1}決下心，是否要和我一起戰到命無
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,450)\blur1}挺起胸，氣揚志高
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,900)\blur1}面對太陽，這就是我們的月之抗爭
Comment: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,### 副歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}往前進，拿下勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}與地上的月光一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}手抓緊，那份自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}即使得要交付性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}往前進，拿下勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.47,0:01:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}與天上的星光一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.70,0:01:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}手抓緊，那份自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}即使得要碎骨粉身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}我們必須向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}才能夠奪得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}伴隨著，天空中，高掛的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}那般燒灼你的命
Comment: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,### 導歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:05.82,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(830,320)\blur1}揮舞著，火紅一般的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:10.10,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,350)\blur1}她緩緩地降落到這土地上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:16.42,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,350)\blur1}她，已沒有，像以前般的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:20.30,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,350)\blur1}她也已經聽不見我的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:25.95,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,450)\blur1}我們倆曾經許下的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:32.15,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,410)\blur1}兩人的共同時光，全部都與光線一併消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:37.90,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,650)\blur1}而就是再怎樣微小的夢想和願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:42.65,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,900)\blur1}也終究是，無法，再現
Comment: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,### 副歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.92,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}大家都，粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.77,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}我的同伴們通通都
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:50.32,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}漸漸地，被燒成灰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.44,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}被地上的陽光包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:55.60,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}大家都，粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:58.44,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}我的同伴無人生還
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:01.00,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}漸漸地，被燒成灰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:06.50,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}被天上的日光照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:12.15,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}那太陽逐漸升起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:14.80,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}暗夜漸漸地消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:22.62,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}伴隨著，天空中，墜落的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:25.59,Daybreaker,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,900)\blur1}現在只剩我一人
Comment: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,### 對話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:33.47,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,300)\blur1}「Luna... Luna...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:36.94,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}請你聽我說... Luna
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:40.77,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}我的聲音，你聽得見吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:44.50,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}現在，是時候使用我的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:47.80,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}我說，你這次不成功不行，是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:51.92,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}全部交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:55.32,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}接受我，掌握我的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.75,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}覺醒你的真正潛能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:02.70,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}要消滅太陽，只有這個方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:05.40,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}就只剩這一條路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:08.04,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}放棄你舊的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:19.75,Nightmare,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,8000)\blur1}並接受『夢魘之月』，你的新名字...」
